L.D.S.K.

The BAU must identify a sniper preying on victims in broad daylight, and attempt to recreate a shooting.

Fade Out

Evidence shows that a series of murders is linked to organised crime, but it also leads Horatio and the team to a pair of film students whose screenplay mirrors the details of the crimes.

Don't Stop the Knight

Mike and KITT are sent on a string of mini-missions by a terrorist; Dr. Graiman and Sarah try to fix a sick robot.
